== 争议 ==
本片原本以一名被哥哥以榮譽死刑殺死的伊朗女子，但被[[美國國家伊朗議會|美國國家伊朗議會]]（NIAC）強烈反對，原因是以不真實、令人反感和這殺人場口被重寫至一宗罪案，將所有「家庭榮譽」去除<ref name="Guardian">[http://film.guardian.co.uk/news/story/0,,2140974,00.html 'Honour killing' screenplay changed after Iranian complaints] {{Wayback|url=http://film.guardian.co.uk/news/story/0,,2140974,00.html |date=20080724022120 }} [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]], August 3, 2007</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.niacouncil.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=854&Itemid=59 | title=No more Iranian American “honor killing” in major Hollywood picture | date=2007-07-30 | publisher=[[National_Iranian_American_Council|National Iranian American Council]] | accessdate=2009-03-14 | archive-date=2008-03-21 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080321100413/http://www.niacouncil.org/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=854&Itemid=59 | dead-url=no }}</ref>等等。

